Package agile.feature

Class ProgramFeature

  • java.lang.Object
    • agile.feature.AgileObject
      • agile.feature.Feature
        • agile.feature.ProgramFeature

  • public class ProgramFeature
extends Feature
    The ProgramFeature class represents a feature that contains other features grouped by project. Different projects are represented by their names. A single project may have one or many features.

      • getProjectSet

        public java.util.Set<Project> getProjectSet​()
        Returns a set of the Projects under this ProgramFeature. At the time of this method call, each Project will have a current size and in-capacity size matching the projects being represented by this ProgramFeature. Note that manipulating this set or the Projects inside has no effect on this ProgramFeature.
        Returns:
        a set of Project objects representing the projects under this ProgramFeature

      • addFeature

        public boolean addFeature​(java.lang.String projectName,
                          Feature feature)
        Adds the specified feature to the specified project under this ProgramFeature. If a project with the specified name does not exist, one will be created. The feature will only be added to an existing project if it that feature is not already present under that project under this ProgramFeature.
        Parameters:
        projectName - the project to which to added the given feature
        feature - the feature to be added to the given project
        Returns:
        true if the given project does not already contain the specified feature

      • addFeaturePercentEntries

        public DataTable addFeaturePercentEntries​(DataTable table)
        Adds this ProgramFeature's feature key, summary, priority score, and percentage of total in-capacity work to the last row of the specified DataTable. This method call assumes the table has a row already inserted and has headers for the previously-mentioned fields.
        Parameters:
        table - the table to which to add the information to
        Returns:
        the specified DataTable
